<div id="pf5ecd" class="pf w5b h340" data-page-no="5ecd"><div class="pc pc5ecd w5b h340"><div class="t m474 x5d h31 y2fbd ff1 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lesson 11 </div><div class="t m5 x10 h31 y3170 ff1 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">î˜‰</div><div class="t m14d9 x67 h31 y3009 ff1 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">March 10-16 </div><div class="t m193b xf h9e y2ca6 ff1 fs23 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How to Do a Bible </div><div class="t m1311 x42 h9e y2be2 ff1 fs23 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Word Study </div><div class="t m11d7 x85 h9e y28b8 ff1 fs23 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&apos;\\N </div><div class="t m190e x5d h1ff y245 ff7 fs31 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath Afternoon </div><div class="t m25c x5d h87 ye0d ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">READ FOR THIS WEEK&apos;S STUDY: Lev. 19:11-16; Psalm 12; </div><div class="t m116b x5d h87 y1454 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Prov. 30:5, 6; Matt. 5:13-16; 20:26; Luke 10:29-42; Rom. 6:15-</div><div class="t m263 x5d h87 y206b ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">23. </div><div class="t m27a x28 h87 y56d ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY TEXT: &quot;And the King will answer and say to </div><div class="t m805 x28 h87 y12a4 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them, &apos;Assuredly, I say to you, inasmuch as you did it to one of </div><div class="t m1322 x28 h87 yfa0 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the least of these My brethren, you did it to Me&apos; &quot; (Matthew </div><div class="t me71 x28 h87 y1236 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">25:40, NKJV). </div><div class="t m45e x4e h87 y1102 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">KEY THOUGHT: </div><div class="t m5f5 x1d h27 y1102 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This lesson seeks to demonstrate the effec-</div><div class="t m107d x5d h27 y1401 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tiveness of Bible word studies. The word we will study is </div><div class="t m64b xc7 h16 ye35 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">service. </div><div class="t m42d x5d h27 y9d3 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">One way the gospel becomes real to others is by acts of kindness, </div><div class="t m12e x5d h27 y6e7 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">compassion, and unselfishness performed by those who value the gift </div><div class="t m801 x5d h27 y1442 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of salvation and fulfill their responsibility to the world. </div><div class="t mf02 x4e h87 y307 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">WHAT IS SERVICE ALL ABOUT? </div><div class="t m7e7 x4c h27 y1abd ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Service can take many </div><div class="t mb35 x5d h27 y460 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forms. It may be practical service to those in need, service of various </div><div class="t m807 x5d h27 ye37 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">kinds for the church, witnessing to the centrality of Jesus in our lives, </div><div class="t m77d x5d h27 y1776 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">or teaching others God&apos;s special message for the last days. Whatever </div><div class="t md8 x5d h27 y5c8 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it is, we place ourselves at God&apos;s disposal to be His instruments. </div><div class="t m319 x5d h27 ybc0 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Service is part of our sanctification; we are set apart to be used by </div><div class="t m320 x5d h27 y14d1 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God. Service can bring peace to families, communities, churches, </div><div class="t m412 x5d h27 y1ac0 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and to our own lives through presenting Jesus as the answer to human </div><div class="t m12e3 x5d h27 y40 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">need. Service implements mercy and justice in our relationships with </div><div class="t m10fe x5d h27 y1eb6 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">others. </div><div class="t m9d0 x5d h27 y1587 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">88 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
